21:13.747 --> 21:19.013
We set goals for the year to come, hoping that this is the year that we actually stick with them.

21:19.354 --> 21:20.776
Maybe you're going to stick to your budget.

21:21.096 --> 21:22.438
Maybe you're going to lose that weight.

21:22.658 --> 21:24.100
