21:24.320 --> 21:25.462
You're going to grow in your faith.

21:25.542 --> 21:28.786
Whatever it is for you, this could be your year.

21:29.026 --> 21:34.920
But to have goals without making plans, I mean, that's basically just making a wish and blowing out the candles.

21:35.381 --> 21:40.794
For us to actually live the life that we want to live, we need more than wishful thinking.

21:41.516 --> 21:42.418
We need plans.

21:42.562 --> 21:49.131
plans to change our habits because the person who runs 10 miles in one day isn't the one who loses the weight.

21:49.451 --> 21:52.996
