22:07.187 --> 22:15.442
It will connect you with the purpose that you were created for and it will make those changes that you want to see in your life a little bit more attainable.

22:15.822 --> 22:23.615
So for everyone, one habit that would impact your life this year would be to simply make attending church a priority.

22:23.936 --> 22:25.138
If you live near campus,

22:25.218 --> 22:25.739
Go there.

22:25.879 --> 22:29.964
If you can't make it or you're an online attender, come hang out with us online.

22:30.065 --> 22:35.332
It will make a huge impact on your spiritual growth or maybe you're new to following Jesus.

22:35.412 --> 22:43.002
Maybe you just made the decision over Christmas and if that's the case and you haven't already, you have to text the word begin to 77888.

22:44.124 --> 22:48.690
We have free resources that we want to give you that will help you get started on your faith.

22:49.378 --> 22:54.532
